{% block text %}
    <h1 class="maso-pruvod-nadpis">Masopust in Roztoky and Únětice</h1>
    <p class="h3 maso-em">16<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;February&nbsp;2019</p>

    <h2>Central Bohemian Museum in Roztoky – the Chateau</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>from 11:00</strong> <a href="/masks" class="maso-em">Mask rental</a> rich costume selection offered by Sdružení Roztoč (only for those who will finish in the circus tent)</li>
        <li><strong>12:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Ceremonial keg tapping of the Masopust festive beer from Únětice brewery</span>;<br>the masques antics and romp starts – theathres, bands, jugglers…</li>
        <li><strong>14:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Coronation of the Queen of Masopust</span> the passing on of the Masopust right, fanfare Krásné&nbsp;fanfáry, <a href="http://localvocal.cz/">Local&nbsp;Vocal</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Parade through Roztoky to Holý&nbsp;Vrch hilltop</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.google.cz/maps/dir/50.1585055,14.3990066/50.1616947,14.3940287/50.1536488,14.3812738/50.151785,14.3708468/50.1614531,14.3743336/@50.1565322,14.3750353,15z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!4m1!3e2?hl=en">The journey map on google maps</a></li>
        <li><strong>14:30</strong> <span class="maso-em">Parade</span> through the Nádražní, Kroupka and the serpentine</li>
        <li><strong>15:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Konopičky</span> at Tyršovo náměstí, walk through Legií and Třešňovka streets</li>
        <li><strong>16:20</strong> <span class="maso-em">Meeting of the parades</span> from Roztoky, Únětice and Suchdol at Holý vrch hilltop;<br>waving of the flags, dancing at the old Holý Vrch heath, the battle of the Bears, the execution of Klibna</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Chapiteau<br><span class="h4">(circus tent near the bus stop "Roztoky–rozcestí Žalov")</span></h2>

    <div class="maso-excursion">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
                <h3 class="h4">Prices</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>CZK 0</strong> children 0–15</li>
                    <li><strong>CZK 230</strong> till 31<sup>st</sup> December 2018</li>
                    <li><strong>CZK 250</strong> till 15<sup>th</sup> February 2019</li>
                    <li><strong>CZK 280</strong> at the door</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
                <h3 class="h4">Advance sale</h3>
                <div class="maso-button">
                    <a href="https://goout.net/cs/jine-akce/masopustni-zabava-v-roztokach-2019/iimud/+vdbgl/" class="maso-button-link">→ Masopust party tickets ←<br>→ advance sale ←</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <ul>
        <li><strong>16:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Open circus tent</span> for all the cold, tired and hungry paraders!</li>
        <li><strong>18:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Magnum Jazz Bigband</span></li>
        <li><strong>20:00</strong> <span class="maso-em">Acrobats</span>: students of CODARTS – University of the Art Rotterdam and AMoC are preparing a special Masopust show with Cecile&nbsp;da&nbsp;Costa. And music by Tygr v Holinkách ("The Tiger in the Galoshes").</li>
